                    <relation name="saws:isDifferentTo" ref="http://purl.org/saws/ontology#isDifferentTo" active="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7479Saalt" passive="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7516MashafaSa"/>
                </listRelation></standOff><text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
                <note>These incipits and the division in textparts are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP02288">Portland, Ethiopic Manuscript Imaging Project, Weiner Codex 282</ref>, ff. 34r-48r.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="title">
                    <label>Title</label>
                    <ab>መጽሐፈ፡ ሰዓልት፡ ጥበቦ፡ ዘረደሽት፡ ካህን፡ ለባዊ፡ ርእሰ፡ ጥበባት፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Husband">
                    <label>Chapter 1 - Concerning a husband and wife</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ብእሲ፡ ወብእሲት፡ ስምከ፡ ወስማ፡ በ፲ወ፭ግ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Prison">
                    <label>Chapter 2 - Concerning prison and anger</label>
                    <ab>፪ አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ቍጥዓ፡ ወሞቅሕ፡ ስምከ፡ ወእምከ፡ ወርኅ፡ ዕለት፡ ዘተእኅዘ።</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Rebel">
                    <label>Chapter 3 - Concerning a rebel (?)</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ሸፋጭ፡</ab>
                    
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Power">
                    <label>Chapter 4 - Concerning the (royal) power</label>
                    <note>According to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/RSEA4WPK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><title level="m">Catalogue of Ethiopian Manuscripts in the British Library acquired since the Year 1877</title><author><forename>Stefan</forename><surname>Strelcyn</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>British Museum</publisher><date>1978</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note><citedRange unit="page">145</citedRange></bibl>, indicated as <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሥልጣን፡ ዘንጉሥ፡</foreign> ("Royal power") in
                        <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient12034">London, British Library, BL Oriental 12034</ref>.</note>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ሥልጣን፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Ages">
                    <label>Chapter 5 - Concerning ages</label>
                    <note>According to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/RSEA4WPK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><title level="m">Catalogue of Ethiopian Manuscripts in the British Library acquired since the Year 1877</title><author><forename>Stefan</forename><surname>Strelcyn</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>British Museum</publisher><date>1978</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note><citedRange unit="page">145</citedRange></bibl>, indicated as <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕድሜ፡ ወዘመን፡</foreign> ("Ages and times") in
                        <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient12034">London, British Library, BL Oriental 12034</ref>.</note>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ እድሜ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Acquisition">
                    <label>Chapter 6 - Concerning the acquisition of things</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ተቀብሎ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="CH">ተ</supplied>፡ ነገር፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Journey1">
                    <label>Chapter 7 - Concerning a journey</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ፍኖት፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Disease1">
                    <label>Chapter 8 - Concerning disease and death</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ደዌ፡ ወ<choice resp="CH"><sic>መአ</sic><corr>ሞ</corr></choice>ት፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Enemy">
                    <label>Chapter 9 - Concerning the coming of enemies</label>
                    <note>According to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/RSEA4WPK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><title level="m">Catalogue of Ethiopian Manuscripts in the British Library acquired since the Year 1877</title><author><forename>Stefan</forename><surname>Strelcyn</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>British Museum</publisher><date>1978</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note><citedRange unit="page">145</citedRange></bibl>, indicated as <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምጽአተ፡ ጸላዒ፡ ወአርበኛ፡</foreign> ("Coming of Enemies and horsemen") in
                        <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient12034">London, British Library, BL Oriental 12034</ref>.</note>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ዘይመጽእ፡ ፀላዒ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Journey2">
                    <label>Chapter 10 - Concerning one who undertakes a long journey</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ዘነገደ፡ ርሑቀ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Food">
                    <label>Chapter 11 - Concerning food</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ሲሳይ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Loss1">
                    <label>Chapter 12 - Concerning the loss of goods</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ጥፍአተ፡ ንዋይ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Hate">
                    <label>Chapter 13 - Concerning hate</label>
                    <note>According to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/RSEA4WPK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><title level="m">Catalogue of Ethiopian Manuscripts in the British Library acquired since the Year 1877</title><author><forename>Stefan</forename><surname>Strelcyn</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>British Museum</publisher><date>1978</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note><citedRange unit="page">145</citedRange></bibl>, indicated as <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፍቅር፡ ወጽልዕ፡</foreign> ("Love and hate") in
                        <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient12034">London, British Library, BL Oriental 12034</ref>.</note>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ጽልዕ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Message">
                    <label>Chapter 14 - Concerning a message</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ መልእክት፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Valuation">
                    <label>Chapter 15 - Concerning the valuation of goods</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ሐሲ<choice resp="CH"><sic>ሰ</sic><corr>በ</corr></choice>፡ ንዋይ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Delivery">
                    <label>Chapter 16 - Whether a woman gives birth to a child or not</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ዘትወልድ፡ ወኢትወልድ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Disease2">
                    <label>Chapter 17 - Concerning disease and death</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ደዌ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Loss2">
                    <label>Chapter 18 - Concerning the loss of goods</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ጥፍአተ፡ ንዋይ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Journey3">
                    <label>Chapter 19 - Concerning a journey</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ መንገድ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Love">
                    <label>Chapter 20 - Concerning love</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ፍቅር፡</ab>
                </div>       
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Priests">
                    <label>Chapter 21 - Concerning priests</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ካህነት፡</ab>
                </div>   
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Coming1">
                    <label>Chapter 22 - Concerning the coming of an event</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ምጽአት፡ ነገር፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Striking">
                    <label>Chapter 23 - Concerning the striking of a servant (?)</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ጐድዮተ፡ ገብር፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Sale">
                    <label>Chapter 24 - Concerning a sale</label>
                    <note>Being no. 21 after <ref target="#Love"/> in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient12034">London, British Library, BL Oriental 12034</ref>.</note>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ሤጥ፡ ወተሣይጦ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Land">
                    <label>Chapter 25 - Concerning the loss of land</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ጥፍአት፡ ሀገር፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Journey4">
                    <label>Chapter 26 - Concerning a journey and divination (?)</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ነጊድ፡ ወሐረስ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Bribery">
                    <label>Chapter 27 - Concerning a bribery (?)</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ሐልየ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Intercourse1">
                    <label>Chapter 28 - Concerning those, who are having intercourse (?) with the royal house</label>
                    <ab>አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡ ዘበዊዕ፡ ቤተ፡ ንጉሥ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:id="Intercourse2">
